Pinoccio,sells,battery,powered,microcontrollers,that,allow,users,to,create,devices,that,can,communicate,wirelessly,with,the,internet,The,Pinnoccio,API,allows,users,to,manage,and,retrieve,information,from,their,devices,It,also,handles,all,of,the,data,storage,protocols,and,architecture,required,making,it,easy,for,web,programmers,to,get,started,with,hardware,based,projects